summary: An Ordinance refunding to Fred Everett the sum of Five Thousand Five Hundred Three and Fifty-two Hundredths ($5,503.52) Dollars, or so much thereof as may be necessary, for the purpose of canceling Certificate of Purchase No. 5294, erroneously and illegally issued under Ordinance No. 22602, for the condemnation of Ninth Avenue West, et al, authorizing the issuance of a warrant therefor, and declaring an emergency.
